        <abstract> 
<p>Discusses whether or not "male" <hi rend="italic">Acropera</hi> bear fruit. JS’s interpretation of <hi rend="italic">Acropera</hi> pollination is ingenious. Pollen-tubes of some cleistogamous flowers germinate in the anthers.</p> 
